00:11:58.217 --> 00:12:00.386  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>The only thing</i>
<i>we can do to assist</i>

143
00:12:00.469 --> 00:12:03.931  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>is put our faith in 009</i>
<i>and keep fighting.</i>

144
00:12:05.766 --> 00:12:08.686  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>Everybody, are you</i>
<i>willing to do that?</i>

145
00:12:08.853 --> 00:12:09.854  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Of course.

146
00:12:10.020 --> 00:12:11.605  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
You better believe it.

147
00:12:11.772 --> 00:12:13.691  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-You can count on us.
-[G.B.] Absolutely.

148
00:12:13.774 --> 00:12:16.193  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
That's the reason
we came here in the first place.

149
00:12:16.277 --> 00:12:18.112  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Joe] Thanks, guys.

150
00:12:18.279 --> 00:12:19.864  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Troublesome creatures.

151
00:12:20.030 --> 00:12:22.366  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
You're nothing more
than a bunch of warm bodies.

152
00:12:22.533 --> 00:12:24.034  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
You think so, huh?!

153
00:12:24.118 --> 00:12:26.954  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
I'll show you warm! [exhaling]

154
00:12:27.121 --> 00:12:29.999  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
You'll see what we troublesome
creatures are made of.

155
00:12:30.166 --> 00:12:32.084  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[yelling]

156
00:12:35.337 --> 00:12:37.089  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[cyborgs grunting]

157
00:12:38.340 --> 00:12:39.717  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Accelerator!

158
00:12:43.053 --> 00:12:44.180  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[cyborgs yell]

159
00:12:47.975 --> 00:12:50.936  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Why can't I accelerate
like I did before?

160
00:12:51.020 --> 00:12:53.105  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[screams]

161
00:12:54.273 --> 00:12:55.274  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Joe!

162
00:12:58.152 --> 00:12:59.320  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Accelerator!

163
00:13:39.235 --> 00:13:41.111  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[gasping]

164
00:13:41.195 --> 00:13:42.863  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[gasps] Catalina.

165
00:13:47.660 --> 00:13:48.911  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Ivan?

166
00:13:51.080 --> 00:13:52.706  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>Wait. This view.</i>

167
00:14:02.132 --> 00:14:05.010  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Emperor gasping]

168
00:14:08.889 --> 00:14:11.392  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
What is this nothingness I see?

169
00:14:15.938 --> 00:14:17.398  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
What was that?

170
00:14:17.481 --> 00:14:19.316  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
What did I see just now?

171
00:14:20.526 --> 00:14:22.570  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
What was that place?

172
00:14:22.736 --> 00:14:23.946  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
The emptiness.

173
00:14:28.951 --> 00:14:30.160  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
What happened?

174
00:14:30.327 --> 00:14:32.538  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Ivan] <i>That is what 009 see</i>s

175
00:14:32.621 --> 00:14:34.164  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>while he's accelerating.</i>

176
00:14:34.248 --> 00:14:36.667  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>It would seem the Emperor</i>
<i>just saw the same thing.</i>

177
00:14:36.834 --> 00:14:38.586  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
How is that possible?

178
00:14:38.669 --> 00:14:39.712  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[wails]

179
00:14:39.795 --> 00:14:41.630  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-[gasping]
-Catalina?

180
00:14:44.341 --> 00:14:47.386  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Is that 009's view
when he accelerates?

181
00:14:47.469 --> 00:14:49.805  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Damn you, Linker.

182
00:14:49.889 --> 00:14:53.017  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
You used your power
on me and 009.

183
00:14:53.100 --> 00:14:54.810  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
You linked our minds.

184
00:14:55.895 --> 00:14:58.397  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
You will regret that decision!

185
00:15:00.733 --> 00:15:03.193  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-[Françoise gasps]
-[Catalina yelling]

186
00:15:03.277 --> 00:15:04.612  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Catalina!

187
00:15:11.327 --> 00:15:12.494  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Catalina!

188
00:15:12.578 --> 00:15:15.831  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[gasping]

189
00:15:15.915 --> 00:15:16.916  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Joe] No, don't!

190
00:15:17.082 --> 00:15:19.460  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[screams]

191
00:15:19.543 --> 00:15:20.586  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Joe] Catalina!

192
00:15:24.381 --> 00:15:26.884  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Catalina, say something.

193
00:15:27.051 --> 00:15:28.093  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[gasps]

194
00:15:30.054 --> 00:15:33.390  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
I'll never forget you,

195
00:15:33.474 --> 00:15:35.142  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
no matter what...

196
00:15:35.225 --> 00:15:36.977  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Joe.

197
00:15:39.021 --> 00:15:41.774  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Catalina!

198
00:15:44.652 --> 00:15:47.029  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
I know that I
wiped her mind clean.

199
00:15:47.112 --> 00:15:49.239  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
How does she remember you?

200
00:15:49.406 --> 00:15:50.866  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
You sad fool.

201
00:15:50.950 --> 00:15:54.870  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Because humans never forget
what's most important to them.

202
00:15:55.037 --> 00:15:57.539  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
To be swayed
by such pointless pity.

203
00:15:57.623 --> 00:15:59.833  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Such a foolish woman.

204
00:15:59.917 --> 00:16:01.919  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[Joe] Bastard.
Don't you have a heart?

205
00:16:02.127 --> 00:16:04.088  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
As to what you mean by a heart,

206
00:16:04.171 --> 00:16:06.840  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
I never really had one
to begin with.

207
00:16:06.924 --> 00:16:08.801  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
These useless sensations
of yours,

208
00:16:08.884 --> 00:16:11.512  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
this "love,"
that makes you weak.

209
00:16:11.679 --> 00:16:14.264  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
No, that's not true.

210
00:16:14.348 --> 00:16:18.394  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Power without heart,
that's only a form of weakness.

211
00:16:29.238 --> 00:16:30.531  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[gasps]

212
00:16:33.742 --> 00:16:35.577  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Why am I not hitting him?

213
00:16:35.744 --> 00:16:37.955  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Ivan] <i>You must sense it, too</i>,

214
00:16:38.038 --> 00:16:40.791  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>the fact</i>
<i>that 009's acceleration</i>

215
00:16:40.874 --> 00:16:43.127  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>is faster than before.</i>

216
00:16:43.293 --> 00:16:47.131  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Don't make me laugh. What good
will mere acceleration do?

217
00:16:47.297 --> 00:16:49.425  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>You still don't understand?</i>

218
00:16:49.508 --> 00:16:52.636  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>Every time</i>
<i>009 uses his Accelerator,</i>

219
00:16:52.720 --> 00:16:55.014  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>he sees that view all alone.</i>

220
00:16:55.097 --> 00:16:56.640  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Emperor] You be quiet, Ivan.

221
00:16:56.724 --> 00:16:57.850  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Ivan gasping]

222
00:17:06.567 --> 00:17:09.945  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Every time he accelerates?
Not possible.

223
00:17:10.029 --> 00:17:11.363  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
There's no way this novice

224
00:17:11.530 --> 00:17:15.367  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
could endure that level
of overwhelming loneliness.

225
00:17:15.534 --> 00:17:17.619  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Joe yells]

226
00:17:18.620 --> 00:17:21.123  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[Ivan] <i>For three millennia,</i>
<i>you've looked down on other</i>s

227
00:17:21.206 --> 00:17:24.543  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>and manipulated them</i>
<i>to serve your needs,</i>

228
00:17:24.626 --> 00:17:27.463  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>but by using his power</i>
<i>of acceleration,</i>

229
00:17:27.546 --> 00:17:30.424  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>009 has lived</i>
<i>many times longer than you</i>

230
00:17:30.507 --> 00:17:33.469  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>and has always accepted</i>
<i>the needs of others.</i>

231
00:17:33.552 --> 00:17:37.139  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>That, in the end,</i>
<i>is what makes him so powerful.</i>

232
00:17:37.306 --> 00:17:39.016  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
What a ridiculous sentiment.

233
00:17:39.099 --> 00:17:41.018  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Do you mean to say
that this cyborg

234
00:17:41.101 --> 00:17:42.644  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
is more powerful than me? Uhh!

235
00:17:43.645 --> 00:17:44.646  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Joe] Why?

236
00:17:44.813 --> 00:17:47.649  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Why isn't time rewinding?

237
00:17:47.816 --> 00:17:52.112  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>009, even if you manage</i>
<i>to exceed the speed of light,</i>

238
00:17:52.196 --> 00:17:53.864  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>there are some things</i>
<i>that happen</i>

239
00:17:53.947 --> 00:17:55.365  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>that you simply cannot change.</i>

240
00:17:55.532 --> 00:17:57.826  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Joe] <i>Then Catalina is really..</i>.

241
00:18:01.538 --> 00:18:03.082  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[gasps]

242
00:18:03.165 --> 00:18:05.250  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
I am done playing with you!

243
00:18:05.334 --> 00:18:06.835  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[cyborgs yell]

244
00:18:09.004 --> 00:18:09.838  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Ivan!

245
00:18:15.052 --> 00:18:16.053  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[gasps]

246
00:18:20.557 --> 00:18:21.850  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Ivan!

247
00:18:23.644 --> 00:18:26.396  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>Are you still planning</i>
<i>to generate that shockwave?</i>

248
00:18:26.563 --> 00:18:28.398  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Don't fight me on this.

249
00:18:28.482 --> 00:18:30.442  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Let's you and I
destroy the world together.

250
00:18:30.526 --> 00:18:32.194  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
That would be fun,
wouldn't it?

251
00:18:32.361 --> 00:18:34.947  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
-Ivan!
<i>-Don't worry.</i>

252
00:18:35.030 --> 00:18:37.491  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>As long as I simply</i>
<i>give in to his will,</i>

253
00:18:37.574 --> 00:18:39.118  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>we can escape destruction.</i>

254
00:18:39.201 --> 00:18:40.953  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[Joe] <i>Are you including</i>
<i>yourself in that</i>?

255
00:18:41.036 --> 00:18:43.622  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
[Ivan] <i>Please, look after</i>
<i>the others for me</i>.

256
00:18:46.834 --> 00:18:48.710  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Joe] <i>I won't let you do this</i>.

257
00:18:57.219 --> 00:18:58.554  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Accelerator!

258
00:19:01.515 --> 00:19:05.352  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Did you abandon your comrades
and escape, 009?

259
00:19:05.519 --> 00:19:07.396  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Attention, cyborgs.

260
00:19:07.479 --> 00:19:09.690  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Take your last breaths
before your destruction.

261
00:19:09.773 --> 00:19:12.359  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
I'm going to reduce this place
to a barren wasteland.

262
00:19:17.823 --> 00:19:19.867  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Joe] It's no use, Emperor.

263
00:19:19.950 --> 00:19:21.702  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
You see,
your goal is never achieved.

264
00:19:21.785 --> 00:19:22.786  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
What was that?

265
00:19:22.953 --> 00:19:25.831  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Moments ago, I saw the future.

266
00:19:25.914 --> 00:19:28.750  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
I went through time
and saw what comes to pass.

267
00:19:33.964 --> 00:19:35.257  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Joe!

268
00:19:44.474 --> 00:19:46.476  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[no audio]

269
00:19:51.106 --> 00:19:53.025  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[gasping]

270
00:19:57.696 --> 00:19:59.615  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[panicked gasping]

271
00:20:03.493 --> 00:20:05.954  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Get me out of here.

272
00:20:06.038 --> 00:20:07.456  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Let me out!

273
00:20:07.539 --> 00:20:08.749  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
[Joe] Impossible.

274
00:20:10.083 --> 00:20:12.711  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
You'll never be able to go back.

275
00:20:12.878 --> 00:20:14.338  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Why not?

276
00:20:14.421 --> 00:20:16.381  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
And how can you
be acting so calm?

277
00:20:16.548 --> 00:20:19.218  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
I've lived on this planet
for 3,000 years,

278
00:20:19.301 --> 00:20:22.054  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
but this fear makes
me tremble with loneliness.

279
00:20:22.137 --> 00:20:24.348  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
How can you possibly
endure this at all?!

280
00:20:25.807 --> 00:20:26.934  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Because.

281
00:20:39.238 --> 00:20:41.949  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Because that is
my mission in life.

282
00:20:50.415 --> 00:20:52.209  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
Joe!

283
00:20:52.292 --> 00:20:54.753  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Ivan, do you know
where he went?

284
00:20:54.920 --> 00:20:57.381  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
